---
import SEO from '../../components/SEO.astro';
import Schema from '../../components/Schema.astro';
import LanguageSwitcher from '../../components/LanguageSwitcher.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';
import '../../styles/tokens.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <!-- Google Tag Manager -->
    <script>(function(w,d,s,l,i){w[l]=w[l]||[];w[l].push({'gtm.start':
    new Date().getTime(),event:'gtm.js'});var f=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0],
    j=d.createElement(s),dl=l!='dataLayer'?'&l='+l:'';j.async=true;j.src=
    'https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtm.js?id='+i+dl;f.parentNode.insertBefore(j,f);
    })(window,document,'script','dataLayer','GTM-WHTQCRZ4');</script>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager -->
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/favicon-32x32.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/favicon-16x16.png">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="/apple-touch-icon.png">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <!-- SEO Meta Tags -->
    <SEO
        title="Sobre Mim"
        description="Parceiro contínuo de IA para PMEs portuguesas. Mapeio negócios para encontrar onde a IA gera mais retorno e construo processos fiáveis e auditáveis que entregam resultados consistentes."
        locale="pt"
    />

    <!-- Structured Data -->
    <Schema type="Organization" />
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <noscript><iframe src="https://www.googletagmanager.com/ns.html?id=GTM-WHTQCRZ4"
    height="0" width="0" style="display:none;visibility:hidden"></iframe></noscript>
    <!-- End Google Tag Manager (noscript) -->
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navigation">
        <a href="/pt" class="logo">luís madeira</a>
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/pt/servicos">Serviços</a>
            <a href="/pt/sobre">Sobre</a>
            <a href="/pt/#contact">Contacto</a>
            <LanguageSwitcher currentPath="/pt/sobre" />
        </div>
        <div class="mobile-menu-toggle">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="about-hero">
        <div class="about-hero-content">
            <div class="hero-text-section">
                <h1>SOBRE MIM</h1>
                <h2>Ajudo empresas a crescer ao resolver o trabalho operacional que as atrasa.</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="hero-image-section">
                <img src="/profile.jpeg" alt="Luís Madeira">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <section class="content-section">
        <div class="content-container">

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>O diferencial</h3>
                <p>A maioria dos consultores de tecnologia pensa em sistemas. Eu penso em modelos de negócio. Antes disto, passei dois anos em Capital de Risco, a avaliar empresas, a perceber unit economics e a descobrir o que realmente impulsiona o crescimento sustentável.</p>
                <p>É essa perspetiva que trago a cada projeto. Não "o que é que a IA pode fazer aqui?" mas "onde é que o investimento paga, qual é o bottleneck que mais importa, e qual é o caminho mais rápido para resultados?" As ferramentas são um meio para um fim.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Como trabalho</h3>
                <p>Começo por mapear as suas operações, não para produzir um relatório, mas para perceber onde o tempo e o dinheiro realmente vão. Depois construo soluções que resolvem os problemas específicos que encontro, testo-as com dados reais, e fico consigo depois do lançamento.</p>
                <p>Cada projeto inclui capacitação da equipa. Construo sistemas que a sua equipa percebe e consegue usar, não caixas negras que criam uma nova dependência.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Percurso</h3>
                <div class="timeline">
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <span class="timeline-date">2025 – Presente</span>
                            <strong>Consultoria de IA & Automação</strong>
                            <span class="timeline-place">Estúdio LM, Porto</span>
                            <p class="timeline-note">A trabalhar com PMEs portuguesas em soluções internas, redesenho de workflows e implementação de IA.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="timeline-item">
                        <div class="timeline-dot"></div>
                        <div class="timeline-content">
                            <span class="timeline-date">2023 – 2025</span>
                            <strong>Venture Capital</strong>
                            <span class="timeline-place">IM Gestão de Ativos</span>
                            <p class="timeline-note">Avaliação de empresas, monitorização de portfólio e análise de modelos de negócio em vários setores.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="content-block">
                <h3>Projetos Paralelos</h3>
                <p>Para além do trabalho com clientes, tenho o <a href="https://www.luxloo.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">LuxLoo</a>, um diretório britânico de trailers sanitários de luxo, e criei a <a href="https://www.sallus.pt" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Sallus</a>, uma marca portuguesa de gel retardante de fogo natural e biodegradável.</p>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="cta-section">
        <div class="cta-content">
            <h2>Vamos falar sobre o seu negócio</h2>
            <p>Diga-me o que o está a travar. Digo-lhe o que posso fazer.</p>
            <div class="cta-links">
                <a href="/pt/ai-contact" class="cta-button">Entrar em contacto</a>
                <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lumadeira" target="_blank" class="cta-button-secondary">LinkedIn</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <script>
        // Mobile Menu Toggle
        const mobileMenuToggle = document.querySelector('.mobile-menu-toggle');
        const navLinks = document.querySelector('.nav-links');

        if (mobileMenuToggle) {
            mobileMenuToggle.addEventListener('click', () => {
                mobileMenuToggle.classList.toggle('active');
                navLinks.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close menu when clicking on a link
            const links = navLinks.querySelectorAll('a');
            links.forEach(link => {
                link.addEventListener('click', () => {
                    mobileMenuToggle.classList.remove('active');
                    navLinks.classList.remove('active');
                });
            });
        }

        // Dropdown navigation
        const dropdownToggle = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-toggle');
        const dropdownMenu = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown-menu');
        const navDropdown = document.querySelector('.nav-dropdown');

        if (dropdownToggle && dropdownMenu) {
            dropdownToggle.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
                navDropdown.classList.toggle('active');
            });

            // Close dropdown when clicking outside
            document.addEventListener('click', () => {
                navDropdown.classList.remove('active');
            });

            navDropdown.addEventListener('click', (e) => {
                e.stopPropagation();
            });
        }
    </script>

    <Footer locale="pt" />
</body>
</html>

<style>
/* Reset & Base Styles */
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

/* design tokens loaded from tokens.css */

body {
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    color: var(--color-text);
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
}

/* Navigation */
.navigation {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 24px 60px;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    background-color: var(--color-bg);
    z-index: 1000;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.logo {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.32px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
}

.nav-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 32px;
    align-items: center;
}

.nav-links a {
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-links a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
}

/* Dropdown Navigation */
.nav-dropdown {
    position: relative;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    color: var(--color-text);
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: -0.48px;
    cursor: pointer;
    padding: 0;
    font-family: var(--font-primary);
    transition: color 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle:hover {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
}

.nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-toggle svg {
    transform: rotate(180deg);
}

.nav-dropdown-menu {
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(100% + 16px);
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 8px;
    min-width: 160px;
    opacity: 0;
    visibility: hidden;
    transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease;
    z-index: 1000;
}

.nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
    opacity: 1;
    visibility: visible;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a {
    display: block;
    padding: 12px 16px;
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 15px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease, color 0.2s ease;
}

.nav-dropdown-menu a:hover {
    background-color: rgba(79, 94, 29, 0.06);
    color: var(--accent-deep);
}

.mobile-menu-toggle {
    display: none;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
    cursor: pointer;
}

.mobile-menu-toggle span {
    width: 32px;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: var(--color-text);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

/* About Hero */
.about-hero {
    padding: 80px 108px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
}

.about-hero-content {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
    gap: 80px;
    align-items: center;
}

.hero-text-section h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 76px;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.76px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.hero-text-section h2 {
    font-size: 28px;
    line-height: 1.4;
    font-weight: 500;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.hero-image-section {
    width: 100%;
    height: 500px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    background-color: var(--paper-2);
}

.hero-image-section img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
}

/* Content Section */
.content-section {
    padding: 80px 108px;
}

.content-container {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.content-block {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
}

.content-block:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.content-block h3 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 32px;
    letter-spacing: -0.32px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text);
}

.content-block p {
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.content-block p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.content-block a {
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
    transition: color 0.2s ease;
}

.content-block a:hover {
    color: var(--accent-deep-hover);
}

.timeline {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 32px;
    margin-top: 24px;
}

.timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 6px;
    top: 8px;
    bottom: 8px;
    width: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
}

.timeline-item {
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
}

.timeline-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.timeline-dot {
    position: absolute;
    left: -32px;
    top: 6px;
    width: 13px;
    height: 13px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--accent-deep);
    border: 2px solid var(--paper);
}

.timeline-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
}

.timeline-content strong {
    font-size: 17px;
    color: var(--ink);
}

.timeline-date {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

.timeline-place {
    font-size: 15px;
    opacity: 0.7;
}

.timeline-note {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-top: 4px;
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

.certs-source {
    margin-bottom: 20px !important;
}

.datacamp-logo {
    height: 48px;
    width: auto;
    border-radius: 4px;
}

.certs-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 12px;
}

.cert-item {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 16px 20px;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 500;
    color: var(--color-text);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-card);
    transition: border-color 0.2s ease;
}

.cert-item:hover {
    border-color: var(--accent-deep);
}

.values-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
}

.values-list li {
    padding-left: 24px;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 17px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    opacity: 0.95;
}

.values-list li::before {
    content: '✓';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    top: 0.16em;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1;
}

/* CTA Section */
.cta-section {
    padding: 120px 108px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    text-align: center;
}

.cta-content {
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.cta-content h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 64px;
    letter-spacing: -0.64px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
}

.cta-content p {
    font-size: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 48px;
    opacity: 0.9;
}

.cta-links {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--on-accent);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.cta-button:hover {
    background-color: #c5db6f;
    transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.cta-button-secondary {
    display: inline-block;
    color: var(--accent-deep);
    padding: 16px 40px;
    border: 1px solid var(--accent-deep);
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: background-color 0.2s ease;
}

.cta-button-secondary:hover {
    background-color: rgba(79, 94, 29, 0.08);
}

/* Responsive Design */
@media (max-width: 1024px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 24px 32px;
    }

    .about-hero {
        padding: 60px 32px;
    }

    .about-hero-content {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 48px;
    }

    .hero-image-section {
        max-width: 500px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 60px 32px;
    }

    .cta-section {
        padding: 80px 32px;
    }
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .navigation {
        padding: 20px 16px;
    }

    .logo {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .nav-links {
        position: fixed;
        top: 76px;
        right: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: calc(100vh - 76px);
        background-color: var(--color-bg);
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: flex-start;
        padding: 40px 0;
        transition: right 0.3s ease;
        border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    }

    .nav-links.active {
        right: 0;
    }

    .nav-links a {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-toggle {
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu {
        position: static;
        transform: none;
        margin-top: 16px;
        border: none;
        background-color: transparent;
        padding: 0;
    }

    .nav-dropdown.active .nav-dropdown-menu {
        display: block;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu:not(.active) {
        display: none;
    }

    .nav-dropdown-menu a {
        font-size: 20px;
        padding: 12px 0;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle {
        display: flex;
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:first-child {
        transform: rotate(45deg) translate(8px, 8px);
    }

    .mobile-menu-toggle.active span:last-child {
        transform: rotate(-45deg) translate(8px, -8px);
    }

    .about-hero {
        padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .hero-text-section h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .hero-text-section h2 {
        font-size: 22px;
    }

    .hero-image-section {
        height: 400px;
    }

    .content-section {
        padding: 40px 16px;
    }

    .content-block h3 {
        font-size: 28px;
    }

    .certs-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .cta-section {
        padding: 60px 16px;
    }

    .cta-content h2 {
        font-size: 48px;
    }

    .cta-content p {
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .cta-links {
        flex-direction: column;
    }

    .cta-button,
    .cta-button-secondary {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 300px;
    }
}
</style>
